*netscape-communicator-4.79-r1 (19 Aug 2002)

  01 Mar 2003; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> :
  Removed libflash plugin and depended on newer netscape-flash package to fix #15751.

  19 Aug 2002; Sascha Schwabbauer <cybersystem@gentoo.org> ChangeLog, netscape-communicator-4.79-r1.ebuild :
  Added -ppc to the keywords.

*netscape-communicator-4.79-r1 (28 Apr 2002)

  28 Apr 2002; Jon Nelson <jnelson@gentoo.org> ChangeLog, netscape-communicator-4.79-r1.ebuild  :
  When unpacking .nif files, make sure to use --no-same-owner
  so they are unpacked as root.
  
*netscape-communicator-4.79 (9 Apr 2002)

  9 Apr 2002; Jon Nelson <jnelson@gentoo.org> ChangeLog, netscape-communicator-4.79.ebuild  :
  The grand re-naming of netscape to netscape-communicator
  
*netscape-4.78 (1 Feb 2002)

  1 Feb 2002; G.Bevin <gbevin@gentoo.org> ChangeLog :
  Added initial ChangeLog which should be updated whenever the package is
  updated in any way. This changelog is targetted to users. This means that the
  comments should well explained and written in clean English. The details about
  writing correct changelogs are explained in the skel.ChangeLog file which you
  can find in the root directory of the portage repository.
